You can paste the full URL or just the access code

What's an access code?

An access code is a unique identifier that allows you to download files shared through AnonShare. You should have received this code from the person sharing the files.

Accepted formats:

https://anonshare.com/download/abc123xyzFull download URL
/download/abc123xyzRelative URL path
abc123xyzJust the access code
